                  </persName>
             (Police-constable B 153). I saw the prisoner running about a quarter of a mile from the house; I suspected all was not right - I took him; he took out his handkerchief, and I saw him clasping something in his hand; I asked what it was, he said "What is that to you?" I found this salt spoon in his hand broken.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
